Source versions only have one bomb site. (Full version 1.6 map coming soon.)


Background story:
Kurdistan builds a water intake on the mountains and plans to build a pipe to Iraq. As an equivalent, Iraq offers weapons of mass destruction. Iran's ultranationalist faction doesn't appreciate these actions and now terrorists and a commando group fighting in the name of USA's forces encounter in the water intake's construction site.
------------------------------------------------------------------------

-Mikko "OEM" Uusitalo-

---------------------
Pulley - Bomb/Defuse
---------------------
 
Counter-Terrorists: Charging the front side. Enter and secure 
the depository and the generators in the old tunnels below.

Terrorists: Coming from the back side. Plant the bomb 
in the depository or near the generators in the old tunnels
and let it explode.
 
Other Notes: There are 2 bomb sides in this mission.
There are 3 ways leading to the old tunnels.

Map size: 31 megabytes
Working time: 4 weeks
Recommended Players: 8

Mapping/Level Design by xTc

PORT

Bomb/Defuse Map for Counter-Strike: Source

CS:S original map creator: Valve Corporation
CS:GO original map creator: MR_R3TR0MAN
CS:S map editor: Niko
Navigation Mesh editor: Meurglis3


High-quality port for CS:S of the unfinished large map for CS:GO de_port_go by MR_R3TR0MAN / Roman Macrery.

About the source map (de_port_go for CS:GO):
   This is a remake of unfairly forgotten map de_port from original Valve's Counter-Strike:Source. The author used original layout and rebuild huge open areas to provide better navigation. So this map feels comfortable for close quarters, and of course for snipers duels. Also, because the factory and industrial theme is getting boring for the last time, the author of the map tried to make more "soft" atmosphere (fine-tune lighting).
   The map looks amazing with countless little details and is a realistic approach to remake the old Port from CSS. The choices of the necessary props and textures has been done with great care.
   However, the published alpha version had a number of significant drawbacks. There were no reflections on objects (CubeMaps were not built). Soundscapes were also lost. In addition, the map was poorly optimized.

About this port (de_port_csgo for CS:S):
   This port contains some design changes compared to the original map, made to give more dynamics to the gameplay, align the game balance and make the movements of bots more smooth. In particular: four new paths were added, lost soundscapes have been restored and missed CubeMaps have been built (reflections have been added). As well as many other small visual changes and improvements were made.

Story:
   Members of the local criminal group intend to prevent economically important sea transport along the Northern coast.
   To do this, they will need to detonate a bomb in one of two critical locations on the port territory.
   However, the well-armed security of the oil carrier company is always stay alert...

Note:
   Large open spaces and a lot of objects placed on the map require a lot of system resources. Performance will depend greatly on the configuration of your computer!

P.S. ~ In the port there is always everything that a real man wants: counterfeit booze, cheap whores and unfriendly dockers :-)

CS:S Map: Bomb/Defuse name: de_port_afterSource author: [RЖB] Blade / rumpelbumpel clan: RumpelBumpel homepage: www.rumpelbumpel.de contact: mapping@rumpelbumpel.de ----------------------------------------------------------- Hi dear CS:S-Gamer, after releasing both dust-maps (de_dust2_afterSource / de_dust_afterSource) here is another part of CounterStrike - afterSource -----------beyond afterSource comes reality--------- I´ve redesigned the map totally, in order to get a well otimimized map. Compared to the old beta-release (0.93), there is in some places a gain of more than 30fps! I´ve decided to wait for releasing final status, after getting more necessary critic! The actuall status of de_port_afterSource is BETA! Ver1.93 Here are some facts and figures about the map "de_port_afterSource" : A lot of high detailed new models (inclusive LOD´s)... new textures (including all normalmaps,partially specularmaps and detail-maps) but basically the same play expiry as it is known in the original map! In the screenshot gallery you can get some impressions of the map and selected models! If you want to get an idea of the realism and the game expiry, download and play the map! VERY IMPORTANT: You have to turn on the color correction in the option menu, under graphics. The map has a color correction entity, which brings up the real athmosphere! Credits: Special thanks to my Wingman Stubu, which spend a lot of time with testing the project! Further thanks to the whole rumpelbumpel-clan! Yours rumpelbumpel visit us at our homepage: www.rumpelbumpel.de
